box model
margin: make space between 2 boxes
boarder: make space in the particular box (kind of box line)
padding: make space between border and ::content

border 3 key style
1.W & h
2.Color
3.line size

Box sizing
Border box & content box

Display option
Flex, grid 

Flex: justify Content 
horizental-
Vertical-

Align Flex items
stretch: left center right 
Gap: make gap between content 

Grid 
use "Fr: fraction units" rather then PX
Grid-template-columns: 1fr, 1fr, 1fr
Grid-template-row: 1fr,1fr,1fr
